{"title":"通过配置hosts文件实现本地域名任意设置","uid":"a491df6c16be0da58cbf425261cb880c","slug":"通过配置hosts文件实现本地域名任意设置","date":"2021-11-29T18:38:34.694Z","updated":"2022-01-03T19:21:21.073Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/通过配置hosts文件实现本地域名任意设置.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>在解决了本地环境搭建的问题后，就开始想着要搭建网站了，但是通常需要以 <code>http://localhost</code> 或者 <code>127.0.0.1</code> 之类的访问本地环境的网站。但是，如果本地放的网站多了，不得不做别的操作，比如端口设置，这就显得有点不那么爽，我还记得之前有看到过可以利用 hosts 文件在本地解析任意域名，例如可以将 <code>www.baidu.com</code> 这个域名变成你的，可以放置任意网站内容</p></blockquote>\n<p>1、修改 hosts 文件</p>\n<p>Windows 系统下，hosts 文件路径在 <code>C:\\Windows\\System32\\drivers\\etc</code> ，其他系统请自行百度。</p>\n<p>打开文件夹下的 <code>hosts</code> 文件进行修改，添加你需要的域名，格式如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;IP&gt; &lt;HOSTNAME&gt;.&lt;DOMAIN&gt; &lt;ALIAS&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">127.0.0.1 www.baidu.com<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>这样就可以在本地将域名解析到 <code>127.0.0.1</code> ，进行网站搭建</p>\n<p>2、域名解析</p>\n<p>可以利用任意网站搭建的程序搭建网站，直接添加域名即可。我使用的是宝塔面板，在新建网站的时候直接添加域名就好，还是比较推荐宝塔面板的，对于我这样的非专业人士十分友好</p>\n","feature":false,"text":" 在解决了本地环境搭建的问题后，就开始想着要搭建网站了，但是通常需要以 http://localhost 或者 127.0.0.1 之类的访问本地环境的网站。但是，如果本地放的网站多了，不得不做别的操作，比如端口设置，这就显得有点不那么爽，我还记得之前有看到过可以利用 hosts...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":528,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Develop","slug":"Develop","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Develop.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Website","slug":"Website","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Website.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"RETICENTAR","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"想做的太多，时间却太少","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Reticentar","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"申请微软E5开发者","uid":"66436ddb14b25c816c3684f3b3722ae4","slug":"申请微软E5开发者","date":"2021-11-29T19:26:29.323Z","updated":"2021-11-29T19:54:47.153Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/申请微软E5开发者.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"注册地址1. 开发人员计划网站